Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:42.40,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}「時間よ止まれ少しだけ…」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.38,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}はじまりはいつだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:51.52,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}もう覚えてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:55.80,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}「それもいいか」ってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.64,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}他愛もない事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:02.24,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}いつだって気がつけば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:06.48,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}笑って泣いたりして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:12.52,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}たまに意地はったりもしたりね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:17.66,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}信号が変われば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:23.26,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}せーので進む行き先（このまま）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:27.16,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}言わなくても（どこまでも）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:30.44,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}行けるよねきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:34.30,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}ドラマチックじゃなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:38.18,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}退屈だと嘆いても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:45.02,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}いつかふと思い出す今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:49.08,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}ロマンチックな言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.66,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}無くていいよだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:02:02.06,DefaultTop,OPJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}「時間よ止まれ少しだけ…」呟いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:42.40,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}「时间啊 请暂停一下吧...」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.38,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}是从什么时候开始的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:51.52,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}我已经记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:55.80,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}我心想「那也没关系」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.64,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}无论何时都会意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:02.24,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}一些不足为道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:06.48,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}夹杂着欢笑与泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:12.52,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}偶尔还带着一些虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:17.66,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}信号灯变换颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:23.26,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}我和你一起前行（就这样）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:27.16,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}彼此心照不宣（天涯海角）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:30.44,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}也一定会抵达的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:34.30,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}即便不算戏剧性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:38.18,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}在感叹着青春无趣时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:45.02,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}会恍然想起这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:49.08,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}即便是没有浪漫的言语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.66,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}也没关系 所以拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:02:02.06,Default,OPCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}我呢喃着「时间啊 请暂停一下吧...」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:13.76,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}茜さす校舎の影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:20.06,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}見つからないはずの青春の端っこに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:25.54,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}少し触れたかも けどすぐ消えちゃうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:29.84,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}君が笑いかけてくれることも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:34.66,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}きれいだね　奇跡って呼んでいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:40.20,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}こんな日々が好きだよ　好きだよ　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:46.76,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}だってずっと続くわけじゃないから　抱きしめるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:51.02,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}子供からちょっと踏み出した春の日に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.30,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}進め　進め　進め　一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:57.62,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}今かすかでたしかな風が吹く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:05.36,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}せめて僕と君の間は世界が少し色づきますように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.06,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}どんなキャンバスを描くかな　どんな未来になるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:12.94,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}わからないけど信じてみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:16.82,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32\pos(480,34.666)}笑顔で手を振ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:16.82,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32\pos(1440,34.666)}じゃあまたねと言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:20.76,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}きっと 明日が少し楽しみになるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.82,0:23:27.96,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}季節の速さに沿って　言葉重ねる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:34.68,DefaultTop,EDJP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}どうかどうか幸せでありますように･･･だね！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:13.76,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}夕阳的余晖描绘出校舍的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:20.06,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}映射出本应回不去的青春模样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:25.54,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}连同你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:29.84,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}稍纵即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:34.66,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}如此绚烂 我能称之为奇迹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:40.20,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}我深爱着这样的日常 万分喜爱 无比眷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:46.76,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}无法长久 所以我倍感珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:51.02,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}像孩提时那般在春日轻轻迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.30,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}启程 出发 前进 步步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:57.62,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}现在 隐约起风了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:05.36,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}至少请让你我交汇的世界染上绚烂的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.06,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}要画出怎样的风景 我们会有怎样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:12.94,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}充满未知但我愿意去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:16.82,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32\pos(480,1045.334)}扬起笑容挥手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:16.82,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32\pos(1440,1045.334)}如果约定了再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:20.76,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}就能更加期待明天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.82,0:23:27.96,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}跟随四季变换的步调 异口同声的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:34.68,Default,EDCN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5.32}请一定一定要幸福…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,纯太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果没事的话可以拜托你去买点东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要买可可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不买可可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那买冰淇淋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不买冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:10.98,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.8,894.2)}第8集「赏花与擦肩而过」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花已经开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你心情很好呢  沙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为明天要和小渚一起赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,便当怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵也会做饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲也要来一起做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅长做饭 就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和小渚一起做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她说想吃你做的黑暗料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是小渚能吃到我做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅是这样也足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油好好准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐也会好好准备的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌 你对姐姐好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,做三明治吗 还是做饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,土豆沙拉和炸鸡也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我去那边一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么大家都去那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,装了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你好呀 诚太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,会有礼貌的打招呼了 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,久 久保同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你快看你快看 哥哥好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好多土豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好厉害呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,确实很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对了诚太 来和沙贵打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才不是都和久保同学打招呼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫诚太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是诚太特别喜欢的漂亮石头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你要给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在看哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,白石哥哥 小渚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵被人叫姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲叫哥哥的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次看到 真新鲜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,少年你土豆装的可真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话能帮我们也装一袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 少年和诚太明天有什么安排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那要和我们一起去赏花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们请你们吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,作为你帮我们装土豆的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,明菜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太也想和沙贵一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太 想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你要说什么 沙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲也没意见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起的话会更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你会来的吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,明天请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲你要来一起做便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经开始做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲自己先开始做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只有小渚一个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你快看 沙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经笑得肚子疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲一直在剥洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她是想要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她好像要做汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,说是想放到便当里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我比小渚更擅长做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一定能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托沙贵来帮帮渚咲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她是第一次做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没人帮她的话  一个人做肯定会失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚小渚 洋葱不用剥这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,做汉堡肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 沙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们先把洋葱切成末
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚会切...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,切的时候要把手握成猫爪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要切洋葱末的话  首先把洋葱对半切开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我来切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是沙贵的错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只是稍微切到了一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 让我们继续做汉堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 汉堡肉是我自己想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到小渚会再次受伤我就很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会做得很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲你不做汉堡肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚正在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我来替她做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 要放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚看起来还想要继续尝试的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我会做汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明想帮小渚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,却让她受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲是因为自己不小心才受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不是沙贵的错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,失败之后的努力才是最重要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,失败之后不轻言放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而是去思考下次怎样才能不犯同样的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,失败也是一种重要的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而经验是我们重要的宝物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,渚咲不是那种会在同一个地方跌倒两次的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这点姐姐我可以保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能再给她一次机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是想自己做汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我一定会注意不切到手指的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然可能会犯其他错误
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明是为了能帮到小渚才开始学做料理的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么能因为一次的失败就让她放弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看来不行的人 其实是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚 我们一起加油 做出好吃的汉堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了沙贵 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你为什么这么想做汉堡肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天就是想做汉堡肉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚是第一次做汉堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚小渚 让我吃一口汉堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要尝尝味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不想把第一次拱手相让啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好多花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花开得正好 真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们占的位置在哪里来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还有小摊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我没吃早饭所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,白石同学你这么期待吃便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个 快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧 白石同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,都舍不得下筷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那么大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来 诚太 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是沙贵做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,土豆沙拉也是沙贵做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太 想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,酒喝的真痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,少年你也快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 稍微有点远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,先吃点别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你想吃这个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直盯着汉堡肉看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,氛围真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐你喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我可还不是你的姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然确实 刚才的渚咲像是别人家的新娘一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还不是你的姐姐哦 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊 明菜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快叫我明菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会叫你纯太的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她是喝醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你不叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不叫的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃小摊的烤鸡肉串
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 白石同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沙贵你看着姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我去买烤鸡肉串
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我去买吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,腿…麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,白石哥哥 真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,久保同学看起来很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,该说那张生气的表情 还是那气场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该不是吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是哥哥不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 要和好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你说要和好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要和好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,久 久保同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是白石同学的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才我是不是态度太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是姐姐不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太 白石同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,白石同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,和好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,白石同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我刚才态度不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,白石同学真的没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,却还是不知道你生气的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你说不是我的错的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是在为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我总是这么迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你为我考虑了这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去买烤鸡肉串吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不抓紧时间的话 沙贵一个人也太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,和好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抓手手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,抓？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,诚太 今天不用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是想抓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就变成这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐刚才说的话你忘记就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来马上就是新学期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会分在同一个班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,白石同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你想和我一起分到一个班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我在问你哥哥想不想和我在一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,和小渚在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
